					</a>
				<: } :><br/>
				We had <: $day_registrations_count :> registrations on the web platform in the last 24 hours.
			</p>
		</div>
	</div>
	<hr class="mg-top--none" />
	<div class="row gw">
		<div class="g third">
			<p><a class="button  full  tall  h1  darkblue" href="<: $u('Admin::Language','index') :>"><i class="icon-globe"></i></a></p>
		</div>
		<div class="g twothirds">
			<h3 class="mg-top--small">Language editor</h3>
			<p>Currently supporting <: $languages_count :> languages, supplying <: $translations_count :> translations with <: $votes_count :> votes.</p>
		</div>
	</div>
	<hr class="mg-top--none" />
	<div class="row gw">
		<div class="g third">
			<p><a class="button full tall h1 blue" href="<: $u('Admin::Token','index') :>"><i class="icon-pencil"></i></a></p>
		</div>
		<div class="g twothirds">
			<h3 class="mg-top--small">Token domain management</h3>
			<p>There are <: $token_domains_count :> domains with <: $tokens_count :> tokens.</p>
		</div>
	</div>
	<hr class="mg-top--none" />
	<div class="row gw">
		<div class="g third">
			<p><a class="button  full  tall  h1  paleblue" href=""><i class="icon-eye-open"></i></a></p>
